CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 2, 1957, page 19, reads: "The Town is Yours... is what Mayor David L. Lawrence seems to be saying as he hands the keys to the city to Roy Wilkins in the Council Chambers of City Hall. Mr. Wilkins, executive secretary of the NAACP addressed a capacity crowd at the annual NAACP Human Rights dinner at the Penn-Sheraton Hotel Monday night. - 'Teenie' Harris Photo."David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Pittsburgh Mayor David L. Lawrence shaking hands and presenting key to NAACP executive secretary Roy Wilkins, in Pittsburgh City Council Chambers, City County Building
